{"tid":1258391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[投票] 你地驚唔驚自己喺示威活動中畀警察拉？(假設只係普通程序咁拘捕，而非黑警暴力拘捕)","createTime":"2019-06-26T05:44:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T11:27:26.000Z","uid":264806,"like":11,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"17ea5c45e70d891f9151aa5167c84f87dfaa23f1","tid":1258391,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:44:39.000Z","msg":"注意：條問題係，假設你只係和平示威，無掟磚頭無武器無暴力行為。你最多係被動式咁坐地下唔肯走(警方面求離開而你坐底不從)。然後警方拘捕你咁唧。警方亦無暴力行為。<br />\n<br />\n唔驚既話畀  正評  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n驚(唔想畀警方拉)既話畀  負評  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想知各位抗爭者既標準係點！因為多數人個底線唔同，對抗政府時個玩法就要改變。"},{"pid":"a174d2c564453fdf9daacebc9ccc56510e20dcc7","tid":1258391,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T06:53:29.000Z","msg":"2:2<br />\n求多D人表態！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">另，我諗起一樣野：<br />\n5年前，佔領運動之初，黃之鋒呼召當晚參與者重奪公民廣場，學生及其它成年示威人士一樣係衝入政總前既公民廣場。一樣係被警方圍住無得走。警方要拉既話，一定有拉得到無得走。而當時學生及其它成年示威人士唔怕。<br />\n然後警方開始放催淚彈果晚，有示威者仍停留在添美道，唔肯走。於是又係被警方圍住無得走。如果警方拘捕，佢地實走唔甩的。但呢班留守添美道既示威者唔怕。</span>"},{"pid":"ec6aedaec779e5575c2b3967a89e5163e1b95dd3","tid":1258391,"uid":81917,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T07:01:10.000Z","msg":"驚，驚到仆街 <br />\n但係點都要出黎 驚驚下就上埋前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd2d43854ae9dd835da95d99310eeba3b3ef0dff","tid":1258391,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T07:10:36.000Z","msg":"死囉  3:8<br />\n原來真係驚架？"},{"pid":"7dfcd0ec8769bff439ce5c24003a7b64fc6d3cda","tid":1258391,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T07:52:03.000Z","msg":"3:11"},{"pid":"bafde504e67c871917559e41ccd692b4c032a30a","tid":1258391,"uid":105059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T07:56:43.000Z","msg":"冇咩好驚<br />\n出得黎預左最壞打算"},{"pid":"6397a4c725072f95b19caaebe0ee3f2760a07348","tid":1258391,"uid":10241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T07:59:09.000Z","msg":"幾年前唔驚<br />\n依家有個仔會驚<br />\n但出得去就唔驚得咁多,會有心理準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07f3164905cb99b5086cde131a5b50ebf9b659dd","tid":1258391,"uid":117886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:00:07.000Z","msg":"驚同唔想係兩回事<br />\n唔驚但係唔想咁投咩"},{"pid":"1f1ff290efcc39aad4bb7d46ed2549e08fd27de5","tid":1258391,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:06:43.000Z","msg":"10 : 29  ，接近1:3咁   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a08c6dbe0b390744efcae7f4138630d1f7a1ec73","tid":1258391,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T10:03:47.000Z","msg":"1:3!!!!"},{"pid":"508e52ca4cf6bfc040b3b474e82a8a9842c513a4","tid":1258391,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T11:27:26.000Z","msg":"嘩超過 1:3"}]}